<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154070445" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;April 1&#x2013;7. Jacob 1&#x2013;4,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
