<title>April 814: The Lord Labors with Us</title>
<link>https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/manual/come-follow-me-for-home-and-church-book-of-mormon-2024/15?lang=eng</link>
<dc:creator><![CDATA[The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints]]></dc:creator>
